{"id":144907,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/科学家远距传输光波包/","date":"2011-04-15T13:40:00Z","modified":"2011-04-15T13:40:00Z","title":"科学家远距传输光波包","content":"<p>今天出版的《科学》杂志报导，日本和澳大利亚的科学家在量子通信领域实现了一大突破，他们成功实现了光波包的远距传输。 远距传输利用量子的纠缠，使两个距离很远的粒子实现即时通讯，一个粒子的变化将会影响到另一个粒子。由日本东京大学Noriyuki Lee领导的团队，让光波包与半数的纠缠粒子联系起来，然后毁灭掉波包及其链接的半数粒子，在另一个地方的剩余纠缠粒子可用于重建光波包。这项技术未来可用于高速和高保真的大量信息传输。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/143738e0/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E8%BF%9C%E8%B7%9D%E4%BC%A0%E8%BE%93%E5%85%89%E6%B3%A2%E5%8C%85&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F04%2F15%2F0724216%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E8%BF%9C%E8%B7%9D%E4%BC%A0%E8%BE%93%E5%85%89%E6%B3%A2%E5%8C%85&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F04%2F15%2F0724216%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/100424516589/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/143738e0/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/100424516589/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/143738e0/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=U7Ie5qeo8mA:R1dbm__XEoI:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=U7Ie5qeo8mA:R1dbm__XEoI:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/143738e0/mf.gif\" />